.IX Header "OPTIONS"
In addition to the command line arguments of the Net::Server::HTTP
base classes you can also set the following options.
.IP "app" 4
.IX Item "app"
Should return a coderef of the \s-1PSGI\s0 application.  Is returned by the
app method.
